      "message": "I mean that dlc_test can\u0027t be enabled if dlc is disabled, correct? So in that case \"dlc \u0026\u0026 dlc_test\" \u003d\u003d \"dlc_test\". And since we\u0027re precisely in the context of \"should we run a DLC test?\", it makes sense to rely on a USE flag that is called dlc_test, at least for now. Does that make sense?",
