      "message": "\u003e\u003e I mean that dlc_test can\u0027t be enabled if dlc is disabled, correct?\n\nThese two USE flags are independent. So it\u0027s possible test-dlc and dummy-dlc are installed while dlcservice is not. Do you mean we somehow have a dependency on these two USE flags? Or instead we rename \"dlc\" on the left side of the line to be \"dlc_test\" (does not seem necessary looking at the naming of other softwaredeps...)?",
